---
import { ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react'
---

<section class="py-24 border-y border-surface-highlight bg-surface/20">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-12">
      <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-sm border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 text-xs font-mono"
        >
          SEPARATE PRODUCT
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
          Argos: Runtime Deviation Signals
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Argos detects <span class="text-white font-medium">when</span> the runtime starts behaving differently
          — not <span class="text-white font-medium">why</span>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted max-w-xl">
          Unlike Tracehound, Argos emits <strong class="text-purple-400"
            >non-authoritative signals</strong
          >. It introduces a new trust boundary and operational responsibility, essentially acting
          as a separate observation layer for behavior occurring <em>outside</em> the request lifecycle.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-4">
          <a
            href="/pricing#argos"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 font-medium group transition-colors"
          >
            Learn about Argos
            <ArrowRight className="ml-2 h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-md">
        <div
          class="relative p-8 border border-surface-highlight bg-background/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-sm"
        >
          <!-- Decoration -->
          <div class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-4 h-4 border-t border-r border-purple-500/50">
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-1 -left-1 w-4 h-4 border-b border-l border-purple-500/50">
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 font-mono text-sm">
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-center text-text-muted border-b border-white/5 pb-2"
            >
              <span>Status</span>
              <span class="text-purple-400">ACTIVE</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-center text-text-muted border-b border-white/5 pb-2"
            >
              <span>Sampling Rate</span>
              <span class="text-white">5.0%</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex justify-between items-center text-text-muted border-b border-white/5 pb-2"
            >
              <span>Drift Detected</span>
              <span class="text-red-400">TRUE</span>
            </div>

            <div class="p-3 bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-300 text-xs mt-4">
              WARN: Event loop lag deviation > 2σ
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
